latestPosts.caption:
Most Bay Area locations have already sold out so we drove 43 miles one way for our Valkyries x Peet’s tumblers and turned the trek into a pitstop before our SunDate. The magic for me is in the chase, not just the find. 🪄🥤💜🪽

I patiently scoured every store’s inventory from the City down to Morgan Hill, back up the map between Fremont and Richmond, then east from Emeryville to Orinda. 

After an exhaustive hunt on the app and hella calls to confirm remaining stock, only TWO locations had availability this morning.

🛍️ @valkyries x @peetscoffee 
📅 2025.07.06 Sunday
#valkyries #ballhalla #peetscoffee #tumbler #drink

Have you seen the new @costco hours posted at your warehouse?

Starting this Monday, June 30, only Executive Members can enter at 9 AM*.

If your warehouse is like mine, we’ve had 9 AM opening for years and it’s so convenient. Depending on the queue outside, they friendly roll the gates up before 845 AM. This new Executive access will be a big shift for the early birds. 

If you’re not an Executive Member yet—will this change tempt you to upgrade?

Closing hours stay the same:
Mon–Fri: 10–8:30
Sat: 9:30–7
Sun: 10–7
*Grace period for Gold Star & Business Members through August 31, 2025.

✨🛒🪪
📍 South San Francisco CA

And just like that, our first born is having his own first born. Congratulations AJ & Angelica! You’re going to be loving, wonderful parents. Little one is already blessed with so much love. 

My prayer for our grandbaby-to-be:

Dear Heavenly Father,
 Thank You for this precious gift of new life. We lift up our unborn grandchild to You, asking for Your protection and care as they grow. 

Surround the baby and parents-to-be with Your love and grace, keeping each of them healthy and safe. Provide them with guidance in each milestone, from the first step to the first words, filling them with wisdom and strength.

Bless our son and daughter-in-law with patience and love, and help all of us - family and loved ones - to support and nurture this child with Your guidance. 

We trust in Your perfect plan, knowing You’ve created this child with purpose. May they grow strong in spirit and always walk in Your light.

We give You all the glory, Lord. In Jesus’ name we pray, Amen.
🥰🥹🙏🏼👶🏻
.
.
.
